name: the shaman
description: A neighbor i have here in my ayahuasca community. She is the descendent of an indigenous tribe from the north of brazil(pernambuco). We traded a healing session for a photo shoot and some custom artwork. I was going through a really difficult moment of my life. I am grateful for her help. It is surprising what people can show you if you let them. If you are willing to open up......   by visionary artist brandon fisher. www.brandonfisher.art
